stors free of the conflicts of interest inherent to the proprietary trading conducted by larger financial advisory firms and superbanks evercore investment management asset management and wealth management managing and investing capital on behalf of a broad range of institutional investors such as corporate and public pension funds endowments foundations insurance companies family offices and highnetworth investors each business is led by senior investment professionals with extensive experience in their field and a significant longterm ownership position in their business core values our professionals act as trusted senior advisors to their clients helping them devise strategies for enhancing shareholder value optimally raising capital to meet investment and growth objectives and proactively bringing new ideas and perspective regarding individual companies industry sectors and global markets evercores clientfirst focus is rooted in an unwavering commitment to our core values excellence uncommonly superior achievement embodied as everyday practice excellence is the guiding principal of everything we do and it is the expectation of all who serve on the evercore team experience excellence is only achieved consistently through the knowledge and wisdom of the industrys most experienced professionals industrybest senior talent are intimately involved with the client relationships and activities they oversee integrity sound character and honesty always return better longterm results integrity means clearly communicating our intent keeping our word and focusing on building longlasting clientdriven relationships independence unencumbered by the conflicts of interest created by trading on proprietary balance sheets evercore is led solely by the best interests of our clients we recommend actions we would pursue were we acting in our clients capacity growth strategies today evercore is a premier independent ma restructuring and strategic advisor a leading provider of nonproprietary capital markets execution and advisory services and an investment advisor of choice we will build on this success through the following strategies continue global expansion global perspective and execution capability are critical to navigating development and investment strategies in todays markets with operations in the us the uk mexico hong kong singapore and brazil and strategic alliances in china japan korea and argentina our reach extends across north and south america europe and asia our global expansion will continue through strategic acquisitions and alliances and where the business environment is receptive to our differentiated model and our clients have or seek to develop a significant presence attract senior talent our success is driven primarily by the quality of our people and their commitment to our clients our business model reputation and strength of brand have proven attractive to the industrys most talented professionals we will continue to add selectively to our professional talent pool further globalizing our advisory services and broadening our research sales and trading market sectors increase assets under management we have carefully developed our investment management businesses into highperforming advisors with exceptional managers and robust client service we will continue to grow assets under management both organically and through acquisitions and alliances that expand longterm value opportunities for our clients the essence of evercore careers intern analyst and associate positionsevercores robust programs for undergraduate and graduate students offer career opportunities we believe are unmatched in the industry including training mentorship activities and handson transaction experiencemore experienced hiresevercores rapid global expansion and growing industry sector coverage requires that we consistently seek and hire exceptionallytalented senior executives to join our teammore  back to top evercore group llc is a member of finra 